  h2 4.2.14) MayBelongsTo

  h3 Arguments
  
  p The 'MayBelongsTo' class method is the same call as 'BelongsTo' except that it set the foreign key to be Optional()
  p It takes the following arguments: 
    bash
      | Resource.MayBelongsTo AnotherResource, [fieldName], [foreignKeyName]
  
    p And returns the Resource
    
  p See the corresponding 
    a(href="") MayBelongsTo
    | documentation for more details
          
